AUTH ROUTES
‚úÖ Signup
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "anuj",
  "email": "anuj@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

‚úÖ Signin
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "anuj@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

üßç AVATAR ROUTES

(Require JWT token in headers)

‚úÖ Create Avatar
POST http://localhost:5000/api/avatar/create
Authorization: Bearer <your_token_here>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "avatarClass": "Warrior",
  "gear": ["Iron Sword", "Wooden Shield"]
}

üìÜ HABIT ROUTES

(Require JWT token in headers)

‚úÖ Create Habit
POST http://localhost:5000/api/habit/create
Authorization: Bearer <your_token_here>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Drink Water",
  "type": "health",
  "target": 8,
  "unit": "glasses"
}

‚úÖ Get All Habits
GET http://localhost:5000/api/habit
Authorization: Bearer <your_token_here

‚úÖ Get One Habit
GET http://localhost:5000/api/habit/1
Authorization: Bearer <your_token_here>

‚úÖ Update Habit
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/habit/1
Authorization: Bearer <your_token_here>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Drink More Water",
  "target": 10
}

‚úÖ Delete Habit
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/habit/1
Authorization: Bearer <your_token_here>